@startuml
autonumber
actor "ATCC" as ATCC
participant "RouteController" as Ctrl
participant "SearchRoutesUseCase" as UC
participant "RouteRepository" as Repo
database "Database" as DB

ATCC -> Ctrl : GET /api/routes?origin=LIS&destination=OPO\n(both params optional)
activate Ctrl

Ctrl -> UC : execute(origin, destination)
activate UC

note right of UC: Converts non-blank strings\nto IATAcode value objects\nNull if param not provided

UC -> Repo : search(origin, destination)
activate Repo
Repo -> DB : SELECT * FROM routes\nWHERE (origin IS NULL OR origin_iata = ?)\nAND (destination IS NULL OR destination_iata = ?)
activate DB
DB --> Repo : list of matching routes
deactivate DB
Repo --> UC : List<Route>
deactivate Repo

note right of UC: Maps each Route\nto RouteResponse DTO

UC --> Ctrl : List<RouteResponse>
deactivate UC

Ctrl --> ATCC : 200 OK (JSON Array)
deactivate Ctrl
@enduml
